mirchi ( kannada : &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2013 indian kannada action masala film written and directed by &lt;unk&gt; shiva . the film features an ensemble cast of mirchi , abhimanyu singh and rajkummar rao in the lead roles . the film 's score and soundtrack are composed by rajan-nagendra . the film is a remake of the telugu film mirchi .